.Dt MICPHY 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm micphy
.Nd Micrel KSZ9021 10/100/1000 PHY driver
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "micphy* at mii? phy ?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver currently supports only Micrel KSZ9021RN PHY.
The driver has a fixup for
.Xr cpsw 4
which requires Gig-E PHYs to adjust RGMII signal timing.
